综上所述,想要达成楼主所需效果,正确的命令应该是
1.
/give @s minecraft:crossbow{Enchantments:[{id:"minecraft:piercing",lvl:5s},{id:"minecraft:multishot",lvl:1s},{id:"minecraft:mending",lvl:1s},{id:"minecraft:quick_charge",lvl:5s}],Unbreakable:1b}
2.
/give @s minecraft:diamond_sword{AttributeModifiers:[{AttributeName:"generic.attackSpeed",Operation:0,Amount:12,UUIDMost:1,UUIDLeast:1,Slot:mainhand},{AttributeName:"generic.attackDamage",Operation:0,Amount:7,UUIDMost:1,UUIDLeast:1,Slot:mainhand}]}
